record FpML5.confirmation.GenericOptionStrike {
  # The price or level at which the option has been struck.
  strikePrice : decimal

  # The price or level expressed as a percentage of the forward starting spot price.
  strikePercentage : decimal

  # The date on which the strike is determined, where this is not the effective date of a forward starting option.
  strikeDeterminationDate : FpML5.confirmation.AdjustableOrRelativeDate?

  # The currency in which an amount is denominated.
  currency : string?

  # The units in which an amount (not monetary) is denominated.
  units : string

}

strikePrice.Doc: The price or level at which the option has been struck.
strikePrice.Name: strikePrice

strikePercentage.Doc: The price or level expressed as a percentage of the forward starting spot price.
strikePercentage.Name: strikePercentage

strikeDeterminationDate.Doc: The date on which the strike is determined, where this is not the effective date of a forward starting option.
strikeDeterminationDate.Name: strikeDeterminationDate

currency.Doc: The currency in which an amount is denominated.
currency.Name: currency

units.Doc: The units in which an amount (not monetary) is denominated.
units.Name: units
